Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.25,0:00:06.54,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Alibi tricks are always uncovered!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.38,0:00:08.88,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The end of a friendship and sorrowful doubts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.55,0:00:11.05,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Happiness just can't be bought.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.38,0:00:13.01,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.01,0:00:14.88,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.88,0:00:15.59,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.56,0:01:47.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Together with Professor Agasa, the Detective Boys went on a camping trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.77,0:01:52.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it was there that we met four university students from an outdoor club with a luxurious camping car...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.69,0:01:54.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fukuura Reiji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.15,0:01:57.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shirafuji Yasumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.45,0:01:59.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tendou Haruka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.53,0:02:02.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Meshiai Takuto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.74,0:02:07.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, while everyone was enjoying the barbecue...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.33,0:02:09.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shirafuji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.67,0:02:14.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To look for her, we took the camping car to a viewing platform on a hill, where fireworks could be seen...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:15.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But she wasn't there either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.88,0:02:18.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, on the way back down...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.93,0:02:20.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the middle of the winding road...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.43,0:02:24.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We discovered Shirafuji Yasumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s body.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.93,0:02:28.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.27,0:02:32.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit must be someone who could take the bicycle from the camping car at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.98,0:02:34.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.15,0:02:40.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The probability that one of Yasumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s three traveling companions was responsible is very high.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.91,0:02:51.62,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,A FRIENDSHIP THAT CAN'T BE BOUGHT\N(PART TWO)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.08,0:02:54.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.42,0:02:57.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do we need to provide alibis?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.38,0:03:00.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't Yasumi's death an accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.26,0:03:01.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just a precaution.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.64,0:03:07.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate, since Yasumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} died between 5:00 and 6:00 PM this evening...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:10.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you please relay what you were doing at that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.14,0:03:14.02,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Tendou Haruka (21)\NCollege Student
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.59,0:03:12.64,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Even if you ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:14.69,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,We were off on our own...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.44,0:03:17.82,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Meshiai Takuto (23)\NCollege Student
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.44,0:03:17.82,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I was fishing alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.61,0:03:21.65,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Fukuura Reiji (21)\NCollege Student
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.61,0:03:21.65,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,No one would be keeping an eye on their watch while camping, would they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.99,0:03:25.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, who was driving the camping car?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:28.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who is the best at it and has been trained, Fukuura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.29,0:03:32.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, if it's just making it move, any of us three could do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.33,0:03:35.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Meishiai and I usually take turns.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:40.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention that Haruka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was the one who drove it to the meeting place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.47,0:03:43.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm, why are you asking us this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.59,0:03:48.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah well, because if you can't drive, you would not be able to move the body to that spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.06,0:03:51.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really are suspecting us, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.52,0:03:52.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.77,0:03:58.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit put Yasumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s body in the middle of the road beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.11,0:04:02.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When ascending the mountain, they acted as if they did not see the body and drove past it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.61,0:04:07.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, on the way down, pretended they had just discovered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:11.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, with so few cars on this mountain road...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.83,0:04:16.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So long as no one is in the passenger seat while the driver goes up the mountain...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.54,0:04:22.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed, it's true that there wasn't anyone in the passenger seat...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.34,0:04:24.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if the angle is changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:28.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The view outside the window will change, and even those in the back will notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.47,0:04:36.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Avoiding a body without changing direction, especially one lying in the middle of the road, just isn't possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.23,0:04:42.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, while passing this place, we opened the sunroof and peered out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.03,0:04:45.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There wasn't anything on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.86,0:04:47.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You looked out the sunroof?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:48.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.84,0:04:52.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we came here last year, we saw fireworks between the mountains after we looked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.41,0:04:56.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why—we just wanted to show the kids as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.62,0:05:00.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we could only see for those ten seconds we were turning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.21,0:05:02.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:06.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you only opened the sunroof after you avoided the corpse...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.69,0:05:09.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't I say that it was impossible to avoid?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.64,0:05:10.35,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.93,0:05:12.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Before or after the sunroof was opened...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.22,0:05:15.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The camper didn't seem to meander.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.18,0:05:18.84,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.65,0:05:22.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's a strange line on one end of the sunroof...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.43,0:05:24.21,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.57,0:05:28.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.24,0:05:31.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.54,0:05:41.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This line is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.63,0:05:47.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:49.43,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The clotted blood took the shape of a line...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.34,0:05:51.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.43,0:05:52.43,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So that's what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.77,0:05:55.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I've solved the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.86,0:05:59.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And this trick requires a high level of skill...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:01.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's that person!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.86,0:06:06.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The flashlight...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:09.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:10.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.28,0:06:12.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.28,0:06:14.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.29,0:06:15.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-Ai...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:17.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:19.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The wind is really strong tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.92,0:06:22.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The camper is also inclined because of the hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:23.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:25.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It isn't bad to be on top of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.47,0:06:30.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You get to see such a beautiful night scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.01,0:06:33.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was right here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:35.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That I saw the fireworks from inside the camper.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.63,0:06:37.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}From here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:38.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:41.31,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}In that case, the trick I thought of just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:43.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.31,0:06:45.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous to climb up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.83,0:06:50.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan-{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.03,0:06:53.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.24,0:06:54.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This isn't good...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:57.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I nearly fell for the culprit's trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.25,0:06:59.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The real trick was...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:06.71,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.13,0:07:07.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:11.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you find something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:11.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:13.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A plastic sheet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:14.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there's blood on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.56,0:07:16.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.39,0:07:18.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:21.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have to hurry and report this to the inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.06,0:07:23.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But this has gotten troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:26.52,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Anyone could have used this trick...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.73,0:07:28.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And there's no evidence that points to the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.24,0:07:31.95,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If that's the case, we can only show them the sheet...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.38,0:07:33.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And observe their reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:35.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.53,0:07:37.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A plastic sheet with blood on it, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:38.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.74,0:07:41.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was at a place about 50 meters from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:42.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Caught on the guardrail.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.83,0:07:45.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:46.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those are definitely blood stains.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.21,0:07:51.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, isn't this the plastic sheet we usually use when camping?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:53.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.63,0:07:55.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I trouble you all to confirm this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:08:00.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It definitely is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.14,0:08:01.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.48,0:08:04.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We haven't used it recently because there's a hole in it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:06.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why is it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.06,0:08:08.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:10.61,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's nothing abnormal about their reactions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.24,0:08:14.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}In that case, I'll have to go look around the mountains for more evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:19.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So that's what it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.66,0:08:22.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The blood got onto the culprit's clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:26.67,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I know the culprit committed the murder in a panic, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.25,0:08:29.71,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It won't be easy to avoid...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:33.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This critical mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:39.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haven't we repeated this a few times?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.93,0:08:44.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we passed by this spot with the camping car at 7:00 PM...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.73,0:08:46.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was nothing on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.73,0:08:49.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was only when we came back two hours later...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.48,0:08:52.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That we found Yasumi in the middle of the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.44,0:08:58.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we were coming up the mountain, all that fell down was the wooden railing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:01.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, didn't that officer just tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:06.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where the railing was damaged and where it landed...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.33,0:09:09.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Formed a straight line with the spot where Yasumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was found.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.25,0:09:13.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And up there at the damaged part of the railings, there were also tire tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:19.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bicycle was also found caught in the trees under the guardrail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:23.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely, when Yasumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} cycled up the mountain...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.06,0:09:26.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means she crashed into them and fell over, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.73,0:09:31.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for why we didn't see Yasumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} on the road while ascending...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.15,0:09:36.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yasumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was caught in the trees at that time, along with the bicycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.74,0:09:38.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She fell down before we descended.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.07,0:09:40.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what you said, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:43.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.95,0:09:46.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, isn't this an accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,0:09:48.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do you insist on suspecting us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.25,0:09:51.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The lack of a blood stain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:54.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There isn't one where Yasumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} initially landed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.76,0:09:58.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she went through the railings and fell down...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.55,0:10:01.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And yet, there's no blood there...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.26,0:10:02.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you find that strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.30,0:10:04.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.56,0:10:05.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means Yasumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} was...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.35,0:10:08.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This point and plastic sheet...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:11.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If this blood stain turns out to be from Yasumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.44,0:10:14.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This will have a vital connection to the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:16.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A very important connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:18.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Agasa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.16,0:10:22.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.41,0:10:26.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With the sunroof closed, it will probably be difficult to hear my deduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.83,0:10:29.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you open the sunroof for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.37,0:10:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:38.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why did you climb onto the roof?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.47,0:10:40.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to experience...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.84,0:10:45.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How the dead Yasumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} felt while being transported this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:56.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How the dead Yasumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} felt while being transported...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:11:02.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you mean that the culprit actually placed Yasumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s corpse on the camper's roof?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:03.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.24,0:11:06.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit pretended to look for Yasumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.41,0:11:08.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And rode with us on this camper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:13.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Along the way, the body on the roof was thrown onto the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:16.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The method used for murdering Yasumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} likely went like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.13,0:11:23.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit first asked Yasumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to get on top of the camper to clean the sunroof.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.84,0:11:27.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, they got behind the one who had fallen for their trap...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:31.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And used a rock or something to hit her head to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.35,0:11:38.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The evidence is this red line on the sunroof.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:43.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit wanted to wipe away the blood left behind after killing Yasumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.24,0:11:45.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this red line was left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.28,0:11:47.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.95,0:11:51.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could Yasumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s body be thrown onto that particular spot?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.37,0:11:55.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All of us were in the camper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:56.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fukuura...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:12:04.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you came upon the broken railing on the road, you were able to brake in time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.55,0:12:06.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:08.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.14,0:12:10.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He made use of the the inertia from the sudden braking...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.52,0:12:14.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To throw the body over the guard rail...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:16.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And have it land on the road below.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.06,0:12:21.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The broken railing was used as a marker for when to brake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.44,0:12:25.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why the body was found on the way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.95,0:12:27.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:30.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are several sharp curves in this area!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.87,0:12:33.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The body would have fallen off if nothing was holding it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:37.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was there rope or tape found near her body?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:39.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:43.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, that lady's belt...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:47.55,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It looks like the one Okino Yoko{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-chan{\r\be10} wears!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.72,0:12:51.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were somethings fluttering on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.39,0:12:53.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, how was it done?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.64,0:12:55.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you didn't notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.56,0:12:59.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of all the decorative tassels on her belt...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:01.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only one had a knot in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:05.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I saw that as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.15,0:13:06.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought it was just something fashionable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.45,0:13:10.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, there is something I forgot to mention.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:11.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Takagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:13.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you close the sunroof for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.66,0:13:14.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:19.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at this line of blood that was just mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:21.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it just a small distance from the edge?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.59,0:13:23.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do you think that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.42,0:13:28.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That must be because, when she was killed, the sunroof was slightly open.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:32.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why did the sunroof need to be slightly open?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:34.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Why"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.43,0:13:35.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.85,0:13:38.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Using the knot on Yasumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s belt that was just mentioned...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.61,0:13:40.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.94,0:13:44.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit held the knot with the sunroof...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:46.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to secure the body in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.45,0:13:49.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why the body was folded into a U-position.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.41,0:13:55.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason the criminal opened the sunroof slightly before the murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.54,0:13:57.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was to allow the murder to be much smoother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:14:02.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they had not done that, after killing Yasumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} on the roof...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.38,0:14:05.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They would have to go back down to open the sunroof from the driver's seat...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.67,0:14:09.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Climb back onto the roof to put the knot in place...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.26,0:14:12.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then finally go back down again to close it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.43,0:14:17.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because the button to open it can only be found on the driver's seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.48,0:14:18.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.64,0:14:23.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You all said that, while ascending the mountain, you opened the sunroof to see the fireworks...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.77,0:14:24.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who opened it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.36,0:14:27.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, it was me—the driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.99,0:14:30.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the one who asked me to open it was Haruka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.61,0:14:31.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.24,0:14:36.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just wanted them to see the great things we did last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.54,0:14:37.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.87,0:14:42.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's so, it's possible to predict someone would want to open it again this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.75,0:14:43.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if that weren't the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:47.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As the driver, it's possible for you secretly open it, if only just a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.60,0:14:49.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.05,0:14:54.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so, you opened the sunroof in order to free the knot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:57.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With the body freed...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:14:59.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could use the inertia from braking near the piece of broken fence...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.89,0:15:02.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To throw the body onto the road below.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.86,0:15:05.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, the only one able to manage this trick...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.52,0:15:09.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would be the one with training and skills as a drift driver, which means it could only be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.11,0:15:11.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think so too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.16,0:15:15.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's actually not the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.24,0:15:19.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, I thought that initially as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.12,0:15:20.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I had missed two points.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.04,0:15:23.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The first is that this stretch of road is uphill.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:27.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The second is that this is the exact place the sunroof was opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.46,0:15:32.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only when I saw the blood stain on the plastic sheet did I think of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.30,0:15:35.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So long as it is in place, below the body...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.80,0:15:38.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The plastic sheet will reduce the friction as a result.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.52,0:15:39.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if nothing else was done...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:42.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The instant the sunroof is opened...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.81,0:15:47.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The body will slide right off the inclined roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.65,0:15:52.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It also means that any of you three could commit the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.82,0:15:55.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.66,0:15:58.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'll have to trouble you by hauling all of you down to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.37,0:16:00.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can find the culprit without doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.46,0:16:04.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because the culprit overlooked the method of wearing clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.88,0:16:05.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The method?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.17,0:16:09.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will you three please stand up for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:11.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:14.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What exactly can you see from this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.05,0:16:18.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.43,0:16:21.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, at her belt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.56,0:16:24.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It hasn't been properly put through the slots in the pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.44,0:16:28.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.11,0:16:29.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.94,0:16:32.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not—I just left home in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.82,0:16:34.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:37.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You took a photo of everyone with your digital camera, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.74,0:16:42.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I recall a picture that caught this lady from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:44.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:45.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not this one...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.96,0:16:47.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.92,0:16:48.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It should be this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.17,0:16:52.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, in the picture, her belt was ran through properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:54.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was in place then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:56.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So why isn't it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.26,0:17:00.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because I took a shower here in the camping car earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.14,0:17:02.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must have been then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:03.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.81,0:17:07.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there a reason to take the belt out of your jeans for a shower?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.31,0:17:10.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because I changed into another pair of jeans.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:13.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Another pair?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.46,0:17:15.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.00,0:17:17.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I see that for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.41,0:17:17.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:22.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These pairs of jeans are pretty similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.16,0:17:25.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The jeans you're wearing in the photo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.87,0:17:27.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the ones you're wearing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.92,0:17:29.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:33.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, excuse me, but may I see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:35.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The jeans you changed out of.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.67,0:17:36.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:39.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't be able to see them even if you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.93,0:17:43.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those were the jeans she wore when she killed Yasumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:47.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Along with the blouse she had on, they've both likely been thrown somewhere on the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:52.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those jeans had Yasumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s blood on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.60,0:17:55.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:17:59.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was her who let us ride the camper to see the fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.70,0:18:00.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.91,0:18:04.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she was using the camper to move the body, why did she let us ride along?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.93,0:18:05.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:08.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She had to let us ride in the camper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.37,0:18:11.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we had followed behind in my car...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.54,0:18:15.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We would see the body fly off, wouldn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.47,0:18:17.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.09,0:18:20.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's the daughter of a rich family...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.85,0:18:23.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not some rich daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.18,0:18:28.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just an ordinary university student from the countryside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.35,0:18:34.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I didn't pretend to be rich, no one would befriend me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.90,0:18:36.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:38.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I worked so hard, and even resorted to getting loans...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:41.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just to rent this expensive camping car...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.53,0:18:43.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we could take it to the mountains or the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.74,0:18:48.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, since they were my first friends, I did my best...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:51.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I thought they were friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.13,0:18:55.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until I heard Yasumi say...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.09,0:19:00.42,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:03.72,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's a complete lie that she's the daughter of a rich family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:06.47,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I noticed it immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.68,0:19:08.68,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I even followed her home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.68,0:19:10.60,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Her apartment was so run-down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.19,0:19:13.94,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Then, we've been deceived for four years?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.43,0:19:18.53,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Then, shouldn't we tell her we know, and ask that she stop pretending?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.08,0:19:21.32,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Isn't she your close friend, Yasumi{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-chan{\r\be10}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.66,0:19:22.78,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Close friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:25.24,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She's only my financial supporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.24,0:19:28.08,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why else would I pretend not to know for four years?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.04,0:19:31.50,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It was tough trying not to laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:34.67,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I mean, if we tell her now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:37.96,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What will we do if she gets angry and asks us to return the money from the past four years?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:39.84,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I don't think she's that kind of person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.59,0:19:43.55,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But Reiji, what a pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.55,0:19:45.39,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Weren't you hoping for a big catch?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.39,0:19:47.10,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Well, I'm disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.43,0:19:49.72,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'll say "bye-bye" after graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:52.73,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But, before then, let's have her keep contributing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.73,0:19:54.81,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This "rich daughter" Haruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.07,0:19:59.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I honestly believed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.28,0:20:03.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I honestly believed we were friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.45,0:20:06.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you killed Yasumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.58,0:20:08.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And framed Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:08.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:11.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got my revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.66,0:20:14.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On that woman who trampled all over "friendship"!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.25,0:20:16.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not a friend at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.67,0:20:22.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were never friends, even from the beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.72,0:20:23.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:26.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's like an automated vending machine for canned juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.51,0:20:30.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll get what you want so long as you have the money, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.31,0:20:32.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You get nothing in return without it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.85,0:20:36.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't buy your way into the hearts of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.75,0:22:25.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that last line that Ai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} came out with was splendid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.67,0:22:26.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.47,0:22:28.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said everything that was in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.51,0:22:31.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara also says the right things when she has to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.43,0:22:32.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.83,0:22:34.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just using what I've learned...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.56,0:22:35.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From a certain someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.35,0:22:41.40,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I think that's usually the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.90,0:22:46.65,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There was a time when Ran rejected an invitation from Sonoko to go skiing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.36,0:22:48.65,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}When I asked her why...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.65,0:22:51.53,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She told me sadly that she didn't have enough pocket money for the month.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.16,0:22:56.37,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}At that time, I asked her why she didn't let Sonoko pay for her, since she's rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.37,0:22:58.75,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She replied to me with anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.66,0:23:01.75,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's out of the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.75,0:23:04.54,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I want to be friends with Sonoko for life!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.55,0:23:06.55,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Or so she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.55,0:23:11.76,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So, to stick around her because she's from a rich family...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.26,0:23:14.55,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And use her money for granted...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.55,0:23:16.10,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It seems the relationships between them are a little fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.06,0:23:21.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you were really cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.35,0:23:22.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-Ai...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.85,0:23:24.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can call me by my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.27,0:23:27.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You wanted to call me that, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.15,0:23:29.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.82,0:23:31.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.95,0:23:37.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.33,0:23:38.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll call you that too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.77,0:23:39.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.25,0:23:41.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.04,0:23:42.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.71,0:23:52.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I wanted to see Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}'s villa in Karuizawa too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.43,0:23:56.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And, besides, that Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.06,0:24:00.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She wouldn't have any great plans anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.94,0:24:02.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.98,0:24:04.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's not in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.15,0:24:17.16,Title,,0,0,0,,SUSPICIOUS CURRY\N(PART ONE)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.16,0:24:22.16,Signs,,0,0,0,,Curry rice
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.68,0:24:20.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Episode's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.21,0:24:22.79,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.79,0:24:23.92,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Tennis after camping!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.92,0:24:25.13,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,A net after a tent!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.13,0:24:27.13,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,And hot curry for adults.
